  <brief_title>Nitazoxanide in Prevention of Secondary Spontaneous Peritonitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Study to Evaluate the Possible Efficacy and Safety of Nitazoxanide in Secondary Prevention of Spontaneous Bacterial Peritonitis in Cirrhotic Patients</official_title>
