  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the study is to evaluate the possible efficacy and safety of nitazoxanide as an adjuvant&#xD;
      therapy in the secondary prevention of SBP in patient with cirrhosis.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      due to high recurrence rate of spontaneous bacterial peritonitis , we will study and evaluate&#xD;
      the possible efficacy and safety of NTZ as an adjuvant therapy in the secondary prevention of&#xD;
      SBP in patient with cirrhosis.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
