             previous confirmed episode of spontaneous bacterial peritonitis.&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Exclusion criteria included active gastrointestinal bleeding Hepatic encephalopathy&#xD;
             (&gt;grade 2) Hepatocellular carcinoma (HCC) or other malignancies Allergy to used&#xD;
             medications.&#xD;
      </textblock>
